X11-FullScreen version 0.01
===========================

Provides a very simple Xlib interface capable of creating borderless
windows taking up an entire screen of an X windows display.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  X11 (www.x.org)
  Imlib2 (http://docs.enlightenment.org/api/imlib2/html/)
  
Building it requires the following Perl modules, available from CPAN:
  Devel::CheckLib
  Module::Build
  ExtUtils::PkgConfig

Testing it requires the following Perl modules, also available from CPAN:
  Test::More
  Test::Kwalitee
  
